    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Dual page illuminated first opening in gold with floral borders (f. 1v-2r); gold floral finispiece (f. 303v); sūrah titles signified by gold bars lined in pink, orange, or blue; textblock border-ruled in red and gold; gold roundels with blue and orange dots mark verse endings; readings in red; floral marginal medallions mark text divisions.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
